                        <interp inst="t18561027-982-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 24.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">The prosecutor stated, that he had received and not paid over, accounts amounting to more than</hi> 20<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.)—<hi rend="italic">
